# HairDrama Task Manager

## Tech Stack

- Frontend: Next.js + TypeScript
- Backend: Flask
- Database: Supabase
- Authentication: Google OAuth
- Email Notifications: Gmail SMTP

## Features

- Google Login
- Create Tasks
- Assign Tasks
- Task Completion
- Notes System
- Edit/Delete Tasks
- Email Notifications

## Architecture

Frontend → Flask API → Supabase Database


## Run Backend

pip install -r requirements.txt
python app.py

## Run Frontend

```bash
npm install
npm run dev


